            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD’s record of his experiments is in DAR 27.1 (ser.7): 1–23.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4">This was probably a response to CD’s letter to the <hi rend="italic">Gardeners’ Chronicle</hi>, 11 April [1855], published on 14 April 1855.</note>
